#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.negative.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.negative"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.negative.negative:1 of
msgid "Numerical negative, element-wise."
msgstr "数值取负，逐元素操作。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.negative.negative of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.negative.negative:3 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.negative.negative:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。如果未提供或"
"为 `None`，将返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.negative.negative:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的原始值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.negative.negative:13 of
msgid ""
"For other keyword-only arguments, see the :ref:`ufunc docs "
"<ufuncs.kwargs>`."
msgstr "对于其他仅关键字参数，请参见 :ref:`ufunc 文档 <ufuncs.kwargs>`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.negative.negative of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.negative.negative:16 of
msgid "**y** -- Returned array or scalar: `y = -x`."
msgstr "**y** -- 返回的数组或标量：`y = -x`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.negative.negative of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

